  <simplesect id="source-docs">
    <title>Source SGML Documentation</title>
    
    <para>The SGML source which generates the <citetitle>Reference
        Guide</citetitle> and the <citetitle>User Guide</citetitle>
        distributions described above, are also available as a
        packages.  You will require the OASIS DocBook DTD and Norman
        Walsh's Modular DocBook Stylesheets, amongst other packages,
        in order to build the distributions like above.  These are
        described in the files <filename
        moreinfo="none">README</filename> and <filename
        moreinfo="none">NEWS</filename> contained within each of these
        packages.</para>
    
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem><para><ulink url="&ftpDocsSrc;swarmdocs-&VERSION;.tar.gz">swarmdocs-&VERSION;.tar.gz</ulink></para></listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para><ulink url="&ftpDocsSrc;userbook-&USERBOOKVERSION;.tar.gz">userbook-&USERBOOKVERSION;.tar.gz</ulink></para>
